data.description: TOP FLOOR UNIT - Spacious 2 bedroom condominium boasts an open floorplan with sunny treetop views! Home features a spacious living room, eat in-in kitchen with pantry closet, a large primary bedroom, spacious second bedroom, and north-facing balcony! Additional highlights include ample closet space throughout, 3rd floor laundry room, detached 1 car garage, newer hot water heater, and  a newer overhead garage door! Home is located near ample shopping, eateries, nature trails, I-80 & I-55, and more! Call today to schedule your home tour!
